MTV Woodies
Awarded for Best emerging music of previous year
Country United States
First awarded November 5, 2004 (2004-11-05)
Website http://www.mtv.com/woodies 
Television/radio coverage
Network MTV

The MTV Woodies (formerly known as the MTVU Woodie Awards) is an annual music show presented by MTVU with awards voted on by fans.
